WEBVTT

00:03:59.256 --> 00:04:01.625
Na sauti ikaita kutoka juu yetu:

00:04:02.269 --> 00:04:03.443
"Amina."

00:04:05.474 --> 00:04:06.628
Ilikua imeisha.

00:04:08.044 --> 00:04:09.346
Nikaangalia saa.

00:04:10.643 --> 00:04:11.936
Ilikua imepita saa sita.

00:04:13.081 --> 00:04:15.018
Nikaangalia waumini wazee

00:04:15.697 --> 00:04:17.565
ambao mwokozi wao hakuja,

00:04:18.045 --> 00:04:21.052
waliokua na majivuno sana kuonyesha
ishara zozote za kusikitika,

00:04:21.052 --> 00:04:23.439
ambao waliamini mengi na kwa mda
mrefu

00:04:23.972 --> 00:04:25.585
kuanza kua na mashaka sasa.

00:04:27.029 --> 00:04:29.842
Lakini nilisikitika kwa niaba yao.